⁣
That people who have a more positive outlook on life are statistically shown to be more healthy?
⁣
Studies have shown that people who look at every situation, every circumstance, and every curve ball life throws in a positive way are more creative, have more genuine friendships and relationships, have less heart disease and strokes, and live longer. 
⁣
I have always been a firm believer that everything happens for a reason. Whether it is something positive or negative. I think that all stems from our mindset. 
⁣
One thing I have learned over the last year of being a coach is how focusing on my own personal development is so important. I now read a chapter of a personal development book every morning and it has been a game changer. 
⁣
Positive actions repeated daily will lead to positive outcomes. Having a positive outlook on LIFE will lead to a more positive life. 
⁣
Whereas being negative, constantly looking at the glass as half empty, and finding something wrong in every situation is going to lead to negative outcomes and a negative, miserable life. 
⁣
We all have hardships, we all have struggles and we all deal with bad situations but it’s how you learn from and turn those struggles around that is going to determine the consequences in your life. 
⁣
Which one are you going to choose?";}i:134;a:1:{s:14:"comments_count";i:5;}i:135;a:1:{s:11:"likes_count";i:11;}i:136;a:1:{s:4:"link";s:39:"https://www.instagram.com/p/CEvFeiLsylo";}i:137;a:1:{s:5:"image";s:249:"https://scontent-sin6-2.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/e35/s1080x1080/118764443_165053755207894_6710360467429724201_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-sin6-2.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=110&_nc_ohc=G94axUWlJ7MAX-htZcA&oh=27e3df3305cabce81fa5794a46152487&oe=5F7D9177";}i:138;a:1:{s:4:"type";s:7:"sidecar";}i:139;a:1:{s:8:"owner_id";i:3553885569;}i:140;a:1:{s:14:"owner_username";s:0:"";}i:141;a:1:{s:14:"owner_fullname";s:0:"";}i:142;a:1:{s:9:"owner_pic";s:0:"";}i:143;a:1:{s:2:"id";s:19:"2391153237935247780";}i:144;a:1:{s:10:"short_code";s:11:"CEvFTN2p9Gk";}i:145;a:1:{s:12:"created_time";i:1599267700;}i:146;a:1:{s:7:"caption";s:1620:"REGISTRASI GELOMBANG KEDUA
